text:
@amerix You have got is partly right.  

The Christian love which couples subscribe to is SELFLESS AND UNCONDITIONAL love.  A man ought to love a woman as he loves himself, causing the wife to love him back.
God loves a man UNCONDITIONALLY, and gives him the capacity to live Him back.

